{
  "stem": "3928.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I was in a ghetto area quite a few times.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, I went through my corridor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never walked through.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, I never walked through.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I just always drove through the ghetto area.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Since the ghetto area was only maybe half a block away where our safe place was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In fact, part of a safe-- the street-- part of a street was the ghetto area, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not where we were, but maybe four houses, you know, of the street.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was a fence was set up for the ghetto there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "A fence area was set up, in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went to-- there were certain places where you can enter with the car, and me, I had no problem, you know, with the German military car to go through the fence, you know?",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the people-- how can I explain to you?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, they did not live there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They existed there only, you know, because [? table-- ?] very little food was available.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And some of the waterworks wasn't working, you know, because they were bombed, you know, and the bombing was done by English and American fliers, you know, during-- the English in daytime and Americans at night.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or-- or I believe-- I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the-- the people were just-- all these 300,000 people were put together to an area which normally would live maybe 30,000.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there were just-- see, this was in October.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The weather wasn't that bad at the time, and by the weather that's so bad, most of them were deported.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But later on, they were deported, most of them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But at the time, you know, in the early days when I was there, you know, one deported.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
